com.jeson.imsdk.video

类 VideoServerConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jeson.imsdk.video.VideoServerConfig

  • public class VideoServerConfig
extends java.lang.Object
    Negotiates signaling for chatting with apprtc.appspot.com "rooms". Uses the client<->server specifics of the apprtc AppEngine webapp. To use: create an instance of this object (registering a message handler) and call connectToRoom(). Once that's done call sendMessage() and wait for the registered handler to be called with received messages.
